♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:21.540
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

00:17:21.660 --> 00:17:25.860
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

00:17:25.900 --> 00:17:27.980
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

00:17:27.980 --> 00:17:29.900
♪Let us meet again♪

00:17:29.910 --> 00:17:35.260
♪One hurried path, and one at ease♪